{"type":"message","id":"3e3b5773","parentId":"bdeb2311","timestamp":"2026-04-24T18:25:54.615Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_px7GDmymgTc8LOoCS6Wh4wtO|fc_0e3c656a6e2a9a630069ebb5b1ab848190851979c15a5e4d7d","toolName":"sessions_history","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:telegram:direct:1477860192\",\n  \"messages\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"Привет\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1777028679368,\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"0f06f420\",\n        \"seq\": 1\n      },\n      \"senderLabel\": \"YuV (1477860192)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"**Crafting a concise response in Russian**\\n\\nI need to respond in a friendly and concise manner in Russian. First, I should consider which of my skills may apply, but it looks like none of them fit the user's greeting of \\\"hello.\\\" Since there’s no specific tool needed, I can just keep it warm and straightforward. I’m focused on making sure my reply feels welcoming!\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"Привет, Юрий. Чем помочь?\",\n          \"textSignature\": \"{\\\"v\\\":1,\\\"id\\\":\\\"msg_0e3c656a6e2a9a630069eb4e4c26008190a39af22978ecbcbd\\\",\\\"phase\\\":\\\"final_answer\\\"}\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-responses\",\n      \"provider\": \"openai\",\n      \"model\": \"gpt-5.4\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1777028679370,\n      \"responseId\": \"resp_0e3c656a6e2a9a630069eb4e48fd688190886d01ab3c0f3888\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"66aa08c5\",\n        \"seq\": 2\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"Проснулся?\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1777046703828,\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"1ae9621e\",\n        \"seq\": 3\n      },\n      \"senderLabel\": \"YuV (1477860192)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"**Replying conversationally**\\n\\nI think I just need to keep my response conversational and a bit playful. There’s no need for tools here, which simplifies things! It’s all about engaging in a friendly way and making it relatable for the user. Having a light-hearted tone might make the interaction more enjoyable. I’ll aim for that balance of being informative while keeping the conversation fun and easy to follow! Let's see how it goes!\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"Да, на месте 🛠️  \\nЧто делаем?\",\n          \"textSignature\": \"{\\\"v\\\":1,\\\"id\\\":\\\"msg_0e3c656a6e2a9a630069eb94b71924819080fb484bad0b812b\\\",\\\"phase\\\":\\\"final_answer\\\"}\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-responses\",\n      \"provider\": \"openai\",\n      \"model\": \"gpt-5.4\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1777046703831,\n      \"responseId\": \"resp_0e3c656a6e2a9a630069eb94b1e87c819086d1f6a56ba3762c\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"e3f3a909\",\n        \"seq\": 4\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"Почему ?\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1777055066137,\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"24446489\",\n        \"seq\": 5\n      },\n      \"senderLabel\": \"YuV (1477860192)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"Потому что я не «бодрствую» как человек непрерывно.  \\nЯ активируюсь, когда приходит сообщение, heartbeat или задача — и дальше уже работаю.\\n\\nТо есть: написал ты → «проснулся» я.  \\nЕсли хочешь, могу ещё объяснить, как это у OpenClaw устроено.\",\n          \"textSignature\": \"{\\\"v\\\":1,\\\"id\\\":\\\"msg_0e3c656a6e2a9a630069ebb561cd6c819084a323c8231ad63a\\\",\\\"phase\\\":\\\"final_answer\\\"}\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-responses\",\n      \"provider\": \"openai\",\n      \"model\": \"gpt-5.4\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1777055066139,\n      \"responseId\": \"resp_0e3c656a6e2a9a630069ebb55e32808190a87e2b25c6dcc9c7\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"6dde4323\",\n        \"seq\": 6\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"Я написал в 8 утра, ответ пришёл в 14:04\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1777055130217,\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"3a820aab\",\n        \"seq\": 7\n      },\n      \"senderLabel\": \"YuV (1477860192)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_1tsyw7nWWiNsKibK4qshJuta|fc_0e3c656a6e2a9a630069ebb5a1a690819086ae16810fe775c5\",\n          \"name\": \"update_plan\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"plan\": [\n              {\n                \"step\": \"Проверить текущее состояние OpenClaw и возможные признаки задержек доставки/обработки\",\n                \"status\": \"in_progress\"\n              },\n              {\n                \"step\": \"Посмотреть историю/сессию, чтобы понять, когда сообщение реально обработалось\",\n                \"status\": \"pending\"\n              },\n              {\n                \"step\": \"Коротко объяснить наиболее вероятную причину с оговоркой по уверенности\",\n                \"status